task.summary: Added prior and altered testing algorithm
Added part 2 training and testing files
Update .gitignore to ignore workspace.xml & update tests to work on Windows (#getamac)
Allow passing of flags from command line to specify training or testing of data
Fix all emails being detected as spam. Number of ham and spam emails were not being saved and so the prior likelihood for each was always being set as 0 during test phase.
Create new test script that runs 10-fold cross validation across the whole data set
